'''No Tears For Ananse''' ni filime yo muri [[Gana]] yayobowe na Sam Aryeetey kandi yanditswe na Ato Kwamina Yanney mu 1968<ref>https://mubi.com/films/no-tears-for-ananse</ref><ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/en/film948213.html</ref>.   

== Umugambi ==
Filime ya rubanda isobanura uburyo amayeri Ananse agerageza kurenza umuryango we kubera igitutu cyo guha umuryango we burimunsi<ref>https://www.allmovie.com/movie/no-tears-for-ananse-v159514</ref><ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b74e2435f</ref>. Yigize nk'uwapfuye abwira umuryango we kumushyingura mu isambu ye<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/no-tears-for-ananse/cast/2000336184/</ref><ref>https://www.cinemagia.ro/filme/no-tears-for-ananse-110230/</ref>, bityo aribwa n'abakozi bashinzwe ibiryo mu murima igihe cyatinze<ref>What actors and actresses appeared in No Tears for Ananse - 1968 ... <nowiki>https://www.answers.com</nowiki> â€º What_actors_and_actresses...</ref>. Umuryango washyizeho umutego ukoresheje igishusho cyometseho kole<ref>https://actoragecheck.com/movie/Kofi-Middleton-Mends/No-Tears-for-Ananse/795568</ref>. Ananse abonye igishusho atekereza ko ari kizima nuko atangira  no gukubitaho urushyi arumirwa. Bukeye bwaho, yafashwe n'umuryango ndetse n'abaturage<ref>http://www.worldcat.org/identities/np-yanney,%20ato%20kwamina</ref>. 

